high_descs: Pick up the spoon from between the plates.
Turn towards the plate on the close seat of the two-seat couch.
Place the spoon onto the closest plate.
Place the plate on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put a Spoon on a Plate and place that Plate on SideTable.

high_descs: Walk ahead to reach the larger sofa.
Pick up the spoon from the couch.
Turn around to face the larger plate.
Put the spoon on the octagonal plate on the couch.
Pick up the plate from the couch.
Walk to the round sidetable on the left of the couch.
Put the plate with the spoon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the Spoon with the Plate on the SideTable.

high_descs:
walk around the sofa 
take the spoon in the table
spoon moves towards the plate 
put the spoon in plate 
take the spoon on the plate along with the plate
walk back to reach the side table 
the plate  place on the side table
anns.task_desc: the plate  place on the side table
